1.0.1.name: wordpress/audiojungle-wordpress-plugin
1.0.1.description: The AudioJungle Wordpress Music Player allows you to embed a dynamic music player in any of your widget areas on your wordpress site. The player allows you to do multiple things such as list search results, top selling files, new files etc. You can include your referral ID to gain commission when prospective buyers click links. Many more features are included, so go ahead and start earning!
